page.title: 16Recreation _ Eling/Millbrook
page.content: When we visited a married couple in Stanton Road, the gentleman told us about his job teaching marine engineering & about his hobbies, water colour painting, collecting model cars and military badges. We found it most interesting. The lady does not have a regular job but she collects very old dolls, sings with a band and is a film extra. {Afternoon At Eling}: Yesterday we went to St. Mary's church, Eling. After we had been inside we went to have a look at the graveyard & then we went to a little beach. I went down the stoney hill & I found some feathers, one big one & the rest little. We climbed a tree & ran down the beach.
